\c 26
\s Valsiraeri, vanogona kurwa, vanoverengwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino denda rakati rapfuura, Jehovha akataura naMozisi naEreazari, mwanakomana womupirisiti Aroni, akati,
\v 2 "Verengai vanhu vose vaIsiraeri, vanamakore ana makumi maviri navanopfuura, nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, vose vanogona kuenda kuhondo pakati paIsiraeri."
\v 3 Mozisi naEreazari mupirisiti vakataura navo pamapani aMoabhu, paJorodhani paJeriko, vakati,
\v 4 "Verengai vanhu vana makore ana makumi maviri navanopfuura; Jehovha sezvakaraira Mozisi navana vaIsiraeri, vakabuda panyika yeIjipiti. "
\p
\v 5 Rubheni ndiye aiva mwanakomana wedangwe waIsiraeri, vanakomana vaRubheni ndivo: Hanoki, kwakabva mhuri yavaHanoki; naParu, kwakabva mhuri yavaParu.
\v 6 NaHezironi, kwakabva mhuri yavaHezironi; naKarimi, kwakabva mhuri yavaKarimi.
\v 7 Ndidzo mhuri dzavaRubheni: Vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi mana nezvitatu, namazana manomwe namakumi matatu.
\v 8 Vanakomana vaParu vaiva Eriabhu;
\v 9 navanakomana vaEriabhu, Nemueri naDhatani naAbhiramu; Dhatani naAbhiramu ndivo vakanga vadanwa kumakurukota, vakarwa naMosesi naAroni paboka raKora, nguva yavakarwa naJehovha,
\v 10 nyika ikashamisa muromo wayo, ikavamedza pamwechete naKora musi wakafa boka iro; nguva iyo moto ukaparadza varume vana mazana maviri namakumi mashanu, vakaitwa chiratidzo.
\v 11 Asi vanakomana vaKora havana kufa.
\p
\v 12 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaSimiyoni, nemhuri dzavo: Nemueri, kwakabva mhuri yavaNemueri, naJamini, kwakabva mhuri yavaJamini, naJakini, kwakabva mhuri yavaJakini;
\v 13 naZera, kwakabva mhuri yavaZera; naShauri, kwakabva mhuri yavaShauri.
\v 14 Ndidzo mhuri dzavaSimiyoni, vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi maviri nezviviri namazana maviri.
\p
\v 15 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaGadhi nemhuri dzavo: Zefoni, kwakabva mhuri yavaZefoni; naHagi, kwakabva mhuri yavaHagi; naShuni, kwakabva mhuri yavaShuni;
\v 16 naZini, kwakabva mhuri yava Zini; naEri, kwakabva mhuri yavaEri;
\p
\v 17 naArodhi, kwakabva mhuri yavaArodhi naAreri kwakabva mhuru yavaAreri.
\p
\v 18 Ndidzo mhuri dzavanakomana vaGadhi; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi mana namazana mashanu.
\p
\v 19 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaJudha: Eri naOnani; asi Eri naOnani vakafira munyika yeKenani.
\v 20 Ndivo vanakomana vaJudha, nemhuri dzavo: Shera, kwakabva mhuri yavaShera; naPerezi kwakabva mhuri yavaPerezi; naZera, kwakabva mhuri yavaZera.
\v 21 Ndivo vanakomana vaPerezi: Hezironi, kwakabva mhuri yavaHezironi; naHamuri, kwakabva mhuri yavaHamuri.
\v 22 Ndidzo mhuri dzaJudha; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi manomwe nezvitanhatu namazana mashanu.
\p
\v 23 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaIsakari, nemhuri dzavo: Tora, kwakabva mhuri yavaTora; naPuva, kwakabva mhuri yavaPuva;
\v 24 naJashubhi, kwakabva mhuri yavaJashubhi, naShimironi, kwakabva mhuri yavaShimironi.
\v 25 Ndidzo mhuri dzalsakari; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi matanhatu nezvina namazana matatu.
\v 26 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaZebhuruni, nemhuri dzavo: Seredhi, kwakabva mhuri yavaSeredhi; naEroni, kwakabva mhuri yavaEroni; naJareeri, kwakabva mhuri yavaJareeri.
\v 27 Ndidzo mhuri dzaZebhuruni; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi matanhatu namazana mashanu.
\p
\v 28 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaJosefa, nemhuri dzavo: Manase naEfuremu.
\v 29 Ndivo vanakomana vaManase: Makiri, kwakabva mhuri yavaMakiri; Makiri wakabereka Gireadhi; kunaGireadhi kwakabva mhuri yavaGireadhi.
\v 30 Ndivo vanakomana vaGireadhi: Jezeri, kwakabva mhuri yavaJezeri; naHereki, kwakabva mhuri yavaHereki;
\v 31 naAsirieri, kwakabva mhuri yavaAsirieri; naShekemu, kwakabva mhuri yavaShekemu;
\v 32 naShemidha, kwakabva mhuri yavaShemidha; naHeferi, kwakabva mhuri yavaHeferi.
\v 33 Asi Zerofehadhi, mwanakomana waHeferi, akanga asina vanakomana, asi vanasikana bedzi; mazita avanasikana vaZerofehadhi aiva Makira, naNoa, naHogira, naMirika, naTiriza.
\v 34 Ndidzo mhuri dzaManase; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi mashanu nezviviri namazana manomwe.
\v 35 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaEfuremu, nemhuri dzavo: Shutera, kwakabva mhuri yavaShutera; naBhekeri, kwakabva mhuri yavaBhekeri, naTahani, kwakabva mhuri yavaTahani.
\v 36 Ndivo vanakomana vaShutera: Erani, kwakabva mhuri yavaErani.
\p
\v 37 Ndidzo mhuri dzavanakomana vaEfuremu; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi matatu nezviviri, namazana mashanu. Ndivo vanakomana vaJosefa, nemhuri dzavo.
\p
\v 38 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaBhenjamini, nemhuri dzavo: Bhera, kwakabva mhuri yavaBhera; naAshibheri, kwakabva mhuri yavaAshibheri; naAhirami, kwakabva mhuri yavaAhirami;
\v 39 naShefufami, kwakabva mhuri yavaShufami; naHufami, kwakabva mhuri yavaHufami.
\v 40 Ndivo vanakomana vaBhera: Aridhi naNamani; kuna Aridhi kwakabva mhuri yavaAridhi; naNamani, kwakabva mhuri yavaNamani.
\v 41 Ndivo vanakomana vaBhenjamini, nemhuri dzavo; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi mana nezvishanu namazana matanhatu.
\p
\v 42 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaDhani, nemhuri dzavo: Shuhami, kwakabva mhuri yavaShuhami. Ndivo vemhuri dzaDhani, nedzimba dzavo.
\v 43 Mhuri dzose dzavaShuhami, vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi matanhatu nezvina namazana mana.
\p
\v 44 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaAsheri, nemhuri dzavo: Imuna, kwakabva mhuri yavaImuna; naIshivhi, kwakabva mhuri yavaIshivhi; naBheria, kwakabva mhuri yavaBheria.
\v 45 Ndivo vanakomana vaBheria: Hebheri, kwakabva mhuri yavaHebheri; naMakieri, kwakabva mhuri yavaMakieri.
\v 46 Zita romwanasikana waAsheri rakanga riri Sera.
\v 47 Ndidzo. mhuri dzaAsheri; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi mashanu nezvitanhatu namazana mana.
\p
\v 48 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaNafutari, nemhuri dzavo: Jazeeri, kwakabva mhuri yavaJazeri; naGuni, kwakabva mhuri yavaGuni;
\v 49 naJezeri, kwakabva mhuri yavaJezeri; naShiremi, kwakabva mhuri yavaShiremi.
\v 50 Ndidzo mhuri dzaNafutari, nemhuri dzavo; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi mana nezvishanu namazana mana.
\p
\v 51 Ndivo vakaverengwa kuvana vaIsiraeri, vakasvika zviuru zvina mazana matanhatu nechiuru chimwe namazana manomwe namakumi matatu.
\p
\v 52 Jehovha akataura naMosesi, akati,
\v 53 "Nyika inofanira kugoverwa pakati paivava, ive nhaka yavo, vachiverengwa namazita avo.
\v 54 Vazhinji unofanira kuvapa nhaka zhinji; vashoma unofanira kuvapa nhaka shoma; mumwe nomumwe unofanira kupiwa sezvavakaverengwa.
\v 55 Kunyange zvakadaro nyika inofanira kugoverwa nemijenya; vachapiwa nhaka namazita amarudzi amadzibaba avo.
\v 56 Nhaka yavo inofanira kugoverwa nemijenya kana vari vazhinji kana vari vashoma."
\p
\v 57 Zvino ndivo vakaverengwa kuvaRevhi, nemhuri dzavo: Gerishoni, kwakabva mhuri yavaGerishoni;. Kohati, kwakabva mhuri yavaKohati; Merari, kwakabva mhuri yavaMerari.
\v 58 Ndidzo mhuri dzavaRevhi: Mhuri yavaRibhini, nemhuri yavaHebhuroni, nemhuri yavaMari, nemhuri yavaMushi, nemhuri yavaKora. Kohati akabereka Amuramu.
\v 59 Zita romukadzi waAmuramu rakanga riri Jokebhedhi, mwanasikana waRevhi, wakaberekerwa Revhi paIjipiti; ndiye wakaberekera Amuramu, Aroni, naMosesi, naMiriami, hanzvadzi yavo.
\v 60 Aroni akaberekerwa Nadhabhi, naAbhihu, naEreazari, naItamari.
\v 61 Nadhabhi naAbhihu vakafa, nguva yavakauyisa moto usina kufanira pamberi paJehovha.
\v 62 Vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi maviri nezvitatu, murume mumwe nomumwe wakanga ano mwedzi mumwe navanopfuura; nokuti havana kuverengwa pakati pavana vaIsiraeri, nokuti havana kupiwa nhaka pakati pavana vaIsiraeri.
\p
\v 63 Ndivo vakaverengwa naMosesi naEreazari mupirisiti, vakaverenga vana vaIsiraeri pamapani aMoabhu, paJorodhani paJeriko.
\v 64 Asi pakati pavo kwakanga kusina murume mumwe wavaya vakaverengwa naMosesi naAroni, vakanga vaverenga vana vaIsiraeri murenje reSinai.
\v 65 Nokuti Jehovha akanga ati napamusoro pavo, "Zvirokwazvo vachafira murenje." Hakuna mumwe wavo akanga asara, asi Karebhu, mwanakomana waJefune, naJoshua, mwanakomana waNuni.
